These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, sprite, milk, 7up
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, traveling, skydiving, singing
1. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking water and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
2. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
3. the person drinking sprite is somewhere between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking water##7
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
6. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | milk | 7up       | sprite | water        |
| Hobby      | skydiving  | traveling | singing        | rock-climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different pets are kept: fish, chinchilla, pony, bird
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, golf, weightlifting, skiing
1. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the owner of the pony##7
2. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the owner of the fish##5
3. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is skiing##5
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
5. the person who's sport is skiing is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person who's sport is golf##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | pony | chinchilla       | bird         | fish     |
| Sport   | golf   | skiing | weightlifting | parkour |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, documentary, satire, thriller
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, hip-hop, punk, jazz
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
2. the fan of jazz is somewhere between the fan of hip-hop and the fan of folk##7
3. the fan of punk is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
4. the fan of folk is somewhere between the fan of jazz and the person watching documentary movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | thriller | satire | martial-arts  |
| Music-Genre   | punk | folk  | jazz   | hip-hop |

