.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, video-games, card-games, magic-tricks
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, swimming, parkour, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##7
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | video-games | rock-climbing | magic-tricks       | card-games |
| Sport   | swimming      | baseball   | parkour | snowboarding  |

