.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, skydiving, board-games, magic-tricks
There are 4 different nationalities: french, spanish, canadian, dutch
1. the dutch is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
2. the french is somewhere to the left of the spanish##5
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
4. the dutch is somewhere between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who's hobby is chess##7
5. the dutch is on the left of the canadian##1
6. the spanish is somewhere to the left of the dutch##5
7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | board-games | chess   | magic-tricks | skydiving |
| Nationality   | french      | spanish | dutch      | canadian |

