.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, fanta, lemonade, soy-milk
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, canadian, indian, colombian
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the indian##1
2. the indian is the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the canadian is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the colombian##3
6. the colombian is somewhere between the japanese and the canadian##7
7. the indian is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | fanta | juice      | lemonade | soy-milk     |
| Nationality   | japanese    | colombian | canadian   | indian |

