.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: french, chinese, turkish, polish
4 different pets are kept: ferret, hedgehog, turtle, goat
1. the chinese is not the owner of the goat##6
2. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
3. the polish is the owner of the turtle##1
4. the turkish is somewhere between the polish and the french##7
5. the chinese is on the left of the french##1
6. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
7. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | polish | turkish | chinese | french |
| Pet           | turtle   | goat    | ferret       | hedgehog  |

