.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, chef, paramedic, fisherman
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, salsa, jazz, funk
1. the project-manager is not the fan of reggae##6
2. the paramedic is on the right of the project-manager##1
3. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the project-manager##3
4. the project-manager is on the right of the fan of funk##1
5. the paramedic is somewhere between the fan of funk and the chef##7
6. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the right of the fan of jazz##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| Job           | fisherman | project-manager | paramedic | chef |
| Music-Genre   | funk         | jazz      | reggae | salsa            |

