.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, scientific, action, zombie
4 different pets are kept: hamster, lizard, hedgehog, goat
1. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere between the person watching disaster movies and the owner of the goat##7
2. the person watching scientific movies is not the owner of the hedgehog##6
3. the owner of the lizard is not the person watching action movies##6
4. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goat##5
5. the person watching disaster movies is the owner of the hamster##1
6. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hamster##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | zombie | scientific | action |
| Pet           | hamster    | lizard   | goat  | hedgehog      |

