2. the fan of classical is on the left of the fan of punk##1
3. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the left of the person watching family movies##5
4. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
5. the person watching romance movies is between the person watching action movies and the fan of d&b##2
6. the fan of classical is somewhere between the fan of d&b and the person watching action movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | romance | action | family   |
| Music-Genre   | d&b    | classical      | punk      | pop |

