3. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
4. the fan of disco is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the fan of folk##5
6. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the fan of disco##1
7. the person drinking juice is the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Beverage      | 7up   | almond-milk | juice | tea   |
| Music-Genre   | funk | disco   | blues | folk |

