3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
4. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the left of the person driving the car##5
5. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
6. the person driving the roller is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |  3   |    4     |
