.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different pets are kept: fish, hedgehog, horse, rat
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, ship, subway, tram
1. the owner of the horse is somewhere between the person driving the van and the owner of the hedgehog##7
2. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
4. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the right of the owner of the horse##5
5. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Pet         | hedgehog    | horse | rat     | fish |
| Transport   | subway | tram  | ship | van |

 